{
  "stem": "11998.5",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He says, you know, he says, you'd never fit under that desk.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I said, yes, I do.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I-- I-- I'll show you.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Come back, I'll show you.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So he-- we-- it was-- it was 10 feet from the door where they-- where the Gestapo was, where the-- where the Nazis were.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he turned around with me, and he marched back to the warehouse.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I lay on the floor, and I put my feet in, and I pulled my body out.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he started laughing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I figure, I had him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And he says, but I'll fire you.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "You're fired.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And that was a big blow, because it was just-- just in the middle of the winter.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And it was very difficult working outside.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "That's the only job that I could get, is we'd go to the Baustelle-- to the construction site.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And he left me in the factory till May, or April.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "When it got warm, I got my notification that I am fired from my job in the factory.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And I had to go out to the-- to the Baustelle.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And-- but the summer was coming, and the weather was good.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I spent the whole summer working outside.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And it was good for me, because I, again, being a little guy--",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was the civilian that we worked for, and he was there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there was a couple.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But the civilian, I kept carrying his lunch bag.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I-- I would-- whatever he wanted, I would do for him, you know?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "When somebody-- when he wanted some attention, I-- I watched him.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Whatever he needed, I would anticipate what he-- what he would need, so that I was always helping him.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he-- he liked that, so he would give me easier jobs.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
